{"type": "article", "id": 25386, "title": "Tiffany 进第三方电商，以及，Jason Wu 推出姊妹品牌｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-04-13T10:39:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 319, "name": "电商"}, {"id": 17448, "name": "蕾丝"}, {"id": 393, "name": "收购"}, {"id": 10, "name": "法国"}, {"id": 25335, "name": "lookbook"}, {"id": 18447, "name": "运动休闲"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 26182, "name": "Sophie Hallette"}, {"id": 26183, "name": "Abercrombie"}, {"id": 1508, "name": "Net-a-porter"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 3814, "name": "Beyonce"}, {"id": 26184, "name": "Cici"}, {"id": 2817, "name": "Jason Wu"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607132704IEsBz67dnoer5H18.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Macy-s-Chief-Marketing-Officer-Martine-Reardon-to-depart-the-company,680785.html#rc\"><b>Macy’s 首席营销官离职</b></a>｜梅西百货（Macy’s ）首席营销官 Martine Reardon 离职，5 月 13 日生效，此前已为梅西效力 32 年，2012 年 2 月担任首席营销官掌管梅西 730 家门店的营销、广告、创意开发、社交媒体、移动端、数字媒体、公关、消费者洞察等等。在她领导下，梅西的营销团队获得了包括艾美奖（Emmys）、克里奥奖（Clios）等诸多荣誉。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Net-A-Porter-and-Tiffany-Co-partner-up,680734.html#rc\"><b>Net-A-Porter 与 Tiffany 开始合作</b></a>｜近日奢侈珠宝品牌 Tiffany &amp; Co. 和奢侈品电商 Net-A-Porter 宣布合作，从 4 月 27 日起，后者成为 Tiffany &amp; Co. 除官网以外的唯一授权线上购买渠道。初步能购买到的仅限于 Tiffany’s T 系列的一些精选商品。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Abercrombie-hires-Ashley-Sargent-Price-as-Creative-Director-of-Marketing,680713.html#rc\"><b>A&amp;F 雇用新市场创意总监</b></a>｜Abercrombie &amp; Fitch 宣布 Ashley Sargent Price 担任公司高级副总裁及市场创意总监，Price 将监督公司旗下所有品牌（包括 Abercrombie &amp; Fitch、Abercrombie 童装和 Hollister Co. ）的营销运作、内部摄影工作室和创意行销。此前她在 J. Crew 担任品牌创意部门的恶高级副总裁，10 年期间掌管 J. Crew 旗下全部品牌包括 J. Crew、Crewcuts 和 Madewell 的创意团队。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Lacemaking-Chanel-acquires-stake-in-Sophie-Hallette,680778.html#rc\"><b>Chanel 投资蕾丝制造商</b></a>｜Chanel 收购法国蕾丝生产商 Sophie Hallette 部分股份，后者现隶属于 Holesco 集团，此前还是 100% 的家庭企业。创立于 1887 年，因悠久历史传承及精湛工艺，凯特王妃的婚礼上所穿的婚纱就选用了这款面料，也曾为一些法国品牌的高级定制系列如 Christian Dior 和 Pierre Balmain 等提供面料。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/jason-wu-collection-grey-jason-wu-10408787/\"><b>Jason Wu 推出姊妹品牌 Grey Jason Wu</b></a>｜周二， Jason Wu 通过 Instagram 宣布推出新品牌 Grey Jason Wu，以他最喜欢的颜色命名，并表示过去的 12 个月都在为其筹备。价格比之前的品牌低一些，在 295－1395 美元之间。6 月就可以在 Jason Wu 的精选门店和 greyjasonwu.com 网站购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132646jpWHog8B6xUGEIAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071326479TbZrz0RjPKgLDnA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132647FfCHOibMcdKhPDay.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132648rPHYjZJk08mznboQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132648u10WsevGNypOqnHa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>英国慈善组织 Fashion Targets Breast Cancer 为庆祝 20 周年，找来超模 Naomi Campbell 和 Kate Moss <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/kate-moss-naomi-campbell-fashion-targets-breast-cancer/\">拍摄了黑白大片</a>，20 年前也是由她们为其出镜。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071326496HCeOMsWvKpQ87XF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132649aCGJzHrEcFfUPmN3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132650Nd8FOH7mnS4XRWAI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">加拿大著名奢侈品电商网站 SSENSE 进军日本，推出日本 SSENSE 网站。找来中国模特项偞婧 Cici <a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/2016/4/sean-and-seng-spring-in-japan-ssense-editorial\">在日本拍摄了一组春日特辑</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132650g4pXPcnwyoWAjEfM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132651As7fTMzueYtq1iwZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132652MBv9hqmFe0sTw8Py.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132652GCcRQyxD03uUvFsl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132652GNFPXIT0sOLrfoqU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132653b7GFWrZPhaNyIeV0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Beyonce 刚推出的个人运动休闲品牌 IVY PARK <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/beyonce-ivy-park-lookbook\">发布春夏系列 lookbook</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132653u2SJVIk7zfg9M3sT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132654p6VSGAfornKWB0vU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713265598qpXUcfdl0Pka2A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">追求钱包极简又实用的，可以看看美国收纳品牌 Postalco 推出的<a href=\"http://postalco.net/products/40001/\">新品 Farmer’s Felt 双折钱包</a>，采用日本植物纤维 Kozo（paper mulberry），比皮革轻许多但很耐用：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132655BuHMeDkwcYsPFI7z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72440945\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132656HFbP8LQY5lNtXJrn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132656ANMq3LpznhG0fakR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72440945\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132657yPF3c5rI1eZa6wOi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72440945\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>庆祝成立 20 周年，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/jimmy-choo-memento/\">Jimmy Choo 推出 MEMENTO 系列</a>，精选历年来红毯系列里的高跟鞋和手袋：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132658GE2MefjdWpvVlBwx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132658mTYevfpyrBi7OQEC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132658DQ8LuHwZiCEtOMjo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132659tuEzohrQYyW7fqj6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713265987J3yU0dGXWRCeqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132700xPI3EhJ0TmkybFd6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">H&amp;M 又一波新品“Canyon Cool”上市， 复古的灵感来自 1970 年代的加州风情：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132700phNEYJgLVmXCfeb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132701AXP0WCq1KlfwvIUj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132701c5W9NiYfbPgpuvzs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132702njiLS2grCR5hXYZy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132702scuTzvRaoyFQLA4U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071327034rXypHjCKvxhs9EY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}